        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

            window.history.back();
        }

                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');

                body3.textContent = ''

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'

                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');

            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');

            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'

            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

            window.history.back();
        }

            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');

            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'

            }

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');

            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        function goBack() {
            window.history.back();
        }

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

            window.history.back();

                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'

            }

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        function goBack() {
            window.history.back();
        }

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

            window.history.back();
        }

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');

            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
    </script>

            window.history.back();

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const title2Div = document.querySelector('.title2');
            if (title2Div && title2Div.textContent.trim() === '{{' + 'ERROR' + '}}') {
                title2Div.textContent = 'We encountered an unexpected error.'
                const titleDiv = document.querySelector('.title');
                if (titleDiv) {
                    titleDiv.textContent = "Sorry, this page can't be found!";
                }
            }
            const body3 = document.querySelector('.body3');
            if(body3?.textContent?.includes('::')){
                body3.textContent = ''
            }
        });
